{
  "stem": "2170.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And also she still worked in the headquarters in the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was going on January, February, 1942.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "March, one night, my sister comes home again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she says to my brother-in-law that she heard that they gave a list again-- the Gestapo-- to put who is going to be alive again and who's going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "With the next, they call it [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Action.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Germany, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister looked over the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she did not see some of my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She start to scream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She went over right away to the-- back to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she told them, how come my mother is not there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My brother summoned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he gave orders right away to put my family back into the list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the morning after that, again, we were taken out in the ghetto-- all of us, whoever was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this time came the Gestapo and that Graf, the head of the Gestapo, Ukrainian police, German border police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they put us in one side, and then they start to read the names.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put us in one side again-- shoemakers, tailors, and the others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the rest who were not doing this kind of work, they put them in the other side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By accident, I supposed to be with my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow I got with the one that was supposed to go to the grave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we were-- I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm already in the line with the one who has to march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they told us, before they kill you, they're going to cut your head off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So better try to get undressed before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I already opened up my shirt.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
